# Cloudflare Turnstile Configuration
# Get these keys from: https://dash.cloudflare.com/?to=/:account/turnstile

# Public site key (safe to expose in client-side code)
NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=0x4AAAAAAA...

# Secret key (server-side only - NEVER expose in client code!)
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY=0x4AAAAAAA...

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://dash.cloudflare.com
# 2. Navigate to Turnstile in the sidebar
# 3. Click "Add Site"
# 4. Enter your domain: heyberkshire.com
# 5. Choose widget mode: "Managed" (recommended) or "Invisible"
# 6. Copy the Site Key → NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY
# 7. Copy the Secret Key → TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY
# 8. Add both to .env.local for development
# 9. Add both to Vercel environment variables for production
#
# Note: Turnstile is FREE and unlimited for all users!
# No credit card or Cloudflare plan required.
